column2: Partly Cloudy.  Winds about 10mph. Dense subsurface macrophyte growth affected accuracy of measurement.  We took measurement at desired GPS reading- but the subsurface growth was so extensive that a open spot was not available anywhere near the desired location.
Sunny day - almost no clouds.  Light winds.  Found open water very near sampling site
Sunny and warm.  Water appears green
some wind- free of aquatic plants
